message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit your needs and expectations. Given its value and quality, I'm extending an exclusive offer to you at a special price of $9,500. This is a unique opportunity to acquire a product worth $10,000 at a discounted rate, tailored specifically for valued customers like yourself. Please let me know if this offer meets your requirements, and we can proceed with the transaction.
